  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "Hell's Horses built this one as a proper upgrade for a new age, not just a refit. Sixty tons, same top speed as the original, six jump jets, and four ER Flamers that will cook anything they get near. Every single Clan ended up running these eventually, even the Homeworld ones. Usually listed as second-line but that label undersells what this thing can do in the right hands. The whole Fire Wasp lineage is something special and this is the biggest version of that idea.",
